author: @abinisaac3613
text: EASY METHOD TO CREATE requirements.txt FOR YOUR PROJECT (WINDOWS)  1) Open your project location and click shift + mouse right click 2) Click  Open power shell window here 3) Type    pip freeze > requirements.txt   and hit enter 4) Your requirements.txt is ready in your project location.
